cài đặt:
https://computingforgeeks.com/how-to-install-postgresql-13-on-ubuntu/

tao user (phai tao superuser de co quyen):
CREATE ROLE rolename LOGIN SUPERUSER PASSWORD 'passwordstring';

truy cập:
sudo -i -u postgres
psql

xem list database:
\l

remote access: https://blog.logrocket.com/setting-up-a-remote-postgres-database-server-on-ubuntu-18-04/
